           SHORT="FUSE filesystem using libarchive"
cat << EOF
Archivemount is a piece of glue code between libarchive and FUSE. It can be used
to mount a (possibly compressed) archive (as in .tar.gz or .tar.bz2) and use it
like an ordinary filesystem.
